                "maximum_value": 1.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The two samples were independently",
                "prepared by different people so as to reduce the",
                "possibility of systematic errors in the sample",
                "thickness. The results with the two samples were",
                "consistent to better than one percent."
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-S",
                "minimum_value": 1.0,
                "maximum_value": 3.0,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " Enough time was spent on each",
                "measurement, both in the center and in the wings, so",
                "that the uncertainty in cross section due to counting",
                "statistics was in the range from one to three",
                "percent. Statistical uncertainties are everywhere",
                "smaller than the diameter of the plotted points."
              ]
            }
